OL,3,CHome Office plans to use more military
OL,4,Csites for asylum accommodation
OL,6,FThe Home Office is planning to use
OL,7,Fmore former military barracks to house
OL,8,Fthousands of asylum seekers, as it
OL,9,Fworks to end the use of hotels for
OL,10,Fsuch accommodation.
OL,12,FIt comes ahead of new immigration
OL,13,Freforms being introduced to parliament
OL,14,Fnext week.
OL,16,FThe government is seeking planning
OL,17,Fpermission for the use of Ministry of
OL,18,FDefence sites in Bicester in
OL,19,FOxfordshire, Barnham in Suffolk and
OL,20,FLinton-on-Ouse in North Yorkshire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
