OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782501495
OL,3,CHome Office plans to use more military
OL,4,Csites for asylum accommodation
OL,6,FThe plan is for these sites to
OL,7,Faccommodate 3,750 asylum seekers in
OL,8,Ftotal.
OL,10,FPlans to use an old RAF base in Linton-
OL,11,Fon-Ouse to house 1,500 asylum seekers
OL,12,Fwere abandoned in 2022, due to
OL,13,Fopposition for local residents and the
OL,14,Fcouncil mounting a legal challenge.
OL,15,FThe decision to revisit those plans
OL,16,Fhas been met with anger from local
OL,17,Fcampaigners.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
