CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782501495
OL,3,CHome Office plans to use more military
OL,4,Csites for asylum accommodation
OL,6,FThe government is also considering
OL,7,Fusing sites in Crowborough, East
OL,8,FSussex and Wethersfeld, Essex for a
OL,9,Flonger period of time.
OL,11,FLabour pledged to end the use of
OL,12,Fasylum hotels by the next election.
OL,14,FAccording to Home Office figures
OL,15,Fpublished last month, the number of
OL,16,Fasylum seekers being housed
OL,17,Ftemporarily in UK hotels has fallen to
OL,18,Fits lowest level since data was first
OL,19,Freported in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
