OL,3,CHome Office plans to use more military
OL,4,Csites for asylum accommodation
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, the Home Office confirmed
OL,12,Fthat 20 more hotels have now been
OL,13,Fclosed, including the Bell hotel in
OL,14,FEpping, which saw protests after hotel
OL,15,Fresident Hadush Kebatu sexually
OL,16,Fassaulted a 14-year-old girl last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
