OL,3,CHome Office plans to use more military
OL,4,Csites for asylum accommodation
OL,6,FBicester and Woodstock MP Calum Miller
OL,7,Fwas shocked over the plans to include
OL,8,Fa former logistics hub in Bicester.
OL,10,F"We need to know about cost, whether
OL,11,Fthis represents value for the
OL,12,Ftaxpayer," he told ITV News Meridian.
OL,14,F"We need to know what will be done to
OL,15,Fprotect local residents, what security
OL,16,Farrangements will be put in place. And
OL,17,Fwhat regime twill be put in place to
OL,18,Fkeep those within the site safe."
OL,26,@rD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
